OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA breezy
OL,6,Fnight with most areas remaining dry
OL,7,Fwith clear spells likely across the
OL,8,Fregion. Southern areas will see risk
OL,9,Fof blustery showers, especially near
OL,10,Fcoasts. Chilly inland by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunshine for Sunday morning
OL,13,Fthen afternoon showers likely, these
OL,14,Fpotentially heavy. A windy day with
OL,15,Ftemperatures mostly around average,
OL,16,Fbut overnight ground frost is possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
